org.freedesktop.wayland.shared

Enum WlShmFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WlShmFormat>
      • org.freedesktop.wayland.shared.WlShmFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WlShmFormat>, HasValue

    public enum WlShmFormat
extends java.lang.Enum<WlShmFormat>
implements HasValue
    pixel formats

    This describes the memory layout of an individual pixel.

    All renderers should support argb8888 and xrgb8888 but any other formats are optional and may not be supported by the particular renderer in use.
